snippet.title: Cute funny animals just never fail to amuse us - Funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
Animals just never fail to amuse us and make us laugh! What could be more entertaining than funny and cute dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, turtles,... What is your favourite clip? ;) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun
